OL,3,CHong Kong convicts 14 pro-democracy
OL,4,Cactivists in national security case
OL,6,FA court in has convicted 14 pro-
OL,7,Fdemocracy activists under a law
OL,8,Fimposed by Beijing aimed at wiping out
OL,9,Fpublic dissent, after widespread anti-
OL,10,Fgovernment protests in 2019.
OL,12,FThe development represents the city's
OL,13,Flargest ever national security case.
OL,15,FThose found guilty of conspiracy to
OL,16,Fcommit subversion, or the act of
OL,17,Foverthrowing or undermining the
OL,18,Fgovernment could face life in prison.
