OL,3,CHong Kong convicts 14 pro-democracy
OL,4,Cactivists in national security case
OL,6,FThey were among 47 people prosecuted
OL,7,Fin 2021 for their involvement with an
OL,8,Funofficial primary election, that
OL,9,F600,000 people voted in while Covid
OL,10,Frestrictions were at their peak.
OL,12,FThe defendants were arrested in dawn
OL,13,Fraids back in January 2021 - many of
OL,14,Fwhom have spent more than three years
OL,15,Fbeing detained.
OL,17,FSome 16 activists and politicians, out
OL,18,Fof the group arrested, decided to
OL,19,Ffight the charges in a trial that has
OL,20,Flasted more than a year.
