OL,3,CHong Kong convicts 14 pro-democracy
OL,4,Cactivists in national security case
OL,6,FTwo of those were acquitted and walked
OL,7,Ffree from court. They were former
OL,8,Fdistrict councilors Lawrence Lau and
OL,9,FLee Yu-shun, who took part in the
OL,10,Funofficial primary held by democrats
OL,11,Fin 2020.
OL,13,FProsecutors accused them of attempting
OL,14,Fto topple the city's leader and
OL,15,Fparalyse its government by securing a
OL,16,Flegislative majority to veto budgets.
