OL,6,FIn documents handed to the media, the
OL,7,Fcourt said the election participants
OL,8,Fhad declared they would "either
OL,9,Factively use or use the power
OL,10,Fconferred on the (legislative council)
OL,11,Fby the (basic law) to veto budgets".
OL,13,FThe verdict showcases how national
OL,14,Fsecurity law has rewritten the city's
OL,15,Fpolitical landscape, with a once
OL,16,Fpermitted pro-democracy opposition now
OL,17,Fstamped out and protest all but erased.
