OL,6,FIt allows for Chinese laws to be valid
OL,7,Fin Hong Kong, and among other things
OL,8,Fit establishes four particular crimes
OL,9,Fthat are punishable with a maximum
OL,10,Fsentence of life in prison.
OL,12,FThese include:
OL,14,FSince its introduction, the city has
OL,15,Fseen the arrest of protesters, former
OL,16,Fopposition politicians and activists.
OL,17,FCivil groups have also been disbanded
OL,18,Fand independent media outlets have
OL,19,Fbeen shut down.
